Congress has clearly defined the boundaries of the FCC’s authority, which do not include acting as a gatekeeper for political speech. The revival of such far-reaching precedents is an alarming step towards undermining free speech and the democratic process.

I strongly urge you to immediately withdraw the proposed rule.

Sincerely,
Ms. Ann Krusec",1561
219,108200899514817,2024-08-20T15:17:27.138Z,Miss Cecelia Farabaugh,,,"Your proposed regulations for AI-generated content in political advertisements would cause significant confusion and directly conflict with established laws. These regulations are not only unnecessary but also detrimental to our democratic process.
