1036,1082540478637,2024-08-25T23:03:34.726Z,Melissa L Spann,,,"I support the FCC's proposal to regulate deepfakes and AI, to create more clarity and understanding for listeners and viewers of content. We need to fully regulate deepfakes and AI on all social media platforms overall, but ESPECIALLY when it comes to candidates and elections!",277
1037,1082520900074,2024-08-25T23:13:26.468Z,Bo Breda,,,"I support the proposal by the FCC to regulate deepfakes and AI, to create more clarity and understanding for listeners and viewers of content, especially when it comes to our elections.  Elections being the bedrock of a democratic republic must be kept immune from fakes of all kinds.  This is a start only.  There are many more restrictions that should be mandated by government concerning AI development.  This should not be allowed to be in the exclusive hands of developers and corporations.",495
