1622,108311035705452,2024-08-31T05:29:49.079Z,Juanita Moser,,,"I support the FCC's proposal to regulate deepfakes and AI, to create more clarity and understanding for listeners and viewers of content, especially when it comes to our elections. Too many lies are being told and displayed. So much fakeness and misinformation and disinformation is being thrown around flagrantly. I am sick and tired of it all. I was taught in school that when I reach adult age I must act like and adult. I now see people 20 years my senior acting like a whining baby and spewing out one lie after another. It is ridiculous and embarrassing.",560
1623,1083192646940,2024-08-31T05:45:34.161Z,Charmian Tashjian,,,"I support the FCC's proposal to regulate deepfakes and AI, to create more clarity and understanding for listeners and viewers of content, especially when it comes to our elections.",180
