1712,10903827305550,2024-09-03T23:00:53.682Z,Lynn Ortenburger,,,"I support the FCC’s proposal to adopt comprehensive, immediate regulations regarding deepfakes and AI content on social media, especially when it comes to our elections, but urgently needed across all social media postings.

We have only to recall the panic created by Orson Welles’ radio broadcast of “War of the Worlds”, which people believed was real. Regulations requiring the labeling of AI content will help create guardrails against the kind of misinformation that can lead to mass hysteria, market crashes, and violent or genocidal acts by human beings who believe themselves to be threatened. Labeling AI content is the least we can do to help prevent the manipulation of human psychological impulses not grounded in reality or fact. 

