9 Id.
10 Id.
11 Id. at 63,387.
12 Safeguarding and Securing the Open Internet, Restoring Internet Freedom, 89 Fed. Reg. 45,404 (May 22, 2024),
https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/FR-2024-05-22/pdf/2024-10674.pdf.
13 Id. at 45,441.
the FCC to expand the current rulemaking to consider comments that would address AI in political
advertising that is disseminated over the internet.
