technologies), and Melanie Magin et al., Campaigning in the Fourth Age of Political Communication. A Multi-
Method Study on the Use of Facebook by German and Austrian Parties in the 2013 National Election
Campaigns, 20 INFO., COMMC’N, & SOC’Y 1698 (2017) (arguing Facebook is an important campaign tool).
