14 See Hany Farid, Creating, Using, Misusing, and Detecting Deep Fakes, 1 J. ONLINE TRUST & SAFETY 1, 3-7
(2022) (discussing the necessary data to create audio, photograph, and video deepfakes).
15 See Birrer and Just, supra note 10 at 5 (“There is, however, no universally accepted definition and studies
diverged in their interpretation of common conceptual elements.”).
