2.3 Election Law
The following discussion on (election) law constitutes the most specific portion of the
literature review, focusing on campaign finance law, lying in elections, the legal implications
of deepfakes, and legal scholarship on deepfakes in elections. The American legal system is
reviewed in Appendix 1.
