means by which the voter… can get the best information.”201 He focuses on addressing
nefarious actors trying to impede election outcomes. These laws are seen as, “a win for voters
and a win for the integrity of our process.”202 Some legislators even described deepfakes as
outright forgeries harming election integrity.203 Therefore, deepfakes heighten election
security risks because they are fraudulent, have the potential to disrupt election integrity and
can be used by foreign adversaries to influence elections.
