74 See Nebraska, 600 U.S. at 504.
75 Id. at 502.
76 Cf. Tiger Lily, LLC v. HUD, 5 F.4th 666, 672 (6th Cir. 2021) (Thapar, J., concurring).
77 Wayman v. Southard, 23 U.S. (10 Wheat.) 1, 42 (1825); U.S. Const. art. I, § 1.
