1800,10918694219080,2024-09-18T16:39:34.927Z,Christopher Hamilton,,,"I reside in California. Following retirement from California civil service as an administrative law judge, I have maintained an active interest in politics. I have worked for many years with the California Clean Money Campaign to urge disclosure of dark money employed to influence political outcomes.

