2069,1091861297758,2024-09-18T23:52:47.843Z,Valerie Bengal,,,"I urge the FCC to adopt and implement, as soon as possible, its proposal for the Disclosure and Transparency of Artificial Intelligence-Generated Content in Political Advertisements.

The pace of technological advances in AI surpasses our ability to evaluate them and to protect the public from disinformation, deep-fakes, and deception by candidates and proponents of political issues. This is now an emergency in our electoral process, given the short time remaining in the campaign season. 

We need transparency and accountability to protect our democratic process. Each time AI is used to make an ad, the FCC process must require a full disclosure. This protection needs to extend beyond the elections to prevent further disinformation and manipulation of the democratic process.

Please implement this proposal right away.",828
2070,1091858872809,2024-09-18T23:58:41.519Z,Cheryl Maslin,,,"I urge the FCC to adopt its proposal on the Disclosure and Transparency of Artificial Intelligence-Generated Content in Political Advertisements as soon as possible.

