Your proposal is a strong step to ensure transparency and the integrity of our democratic process. Please adopt it without delay. Thank you for your time.",718
2071,1091976893336,2024-09-19T00:09:22.502Z,BJ Moore,,,"I urge the FCC to adopt the proposal on Disclosure and Transparency of Artificial Intelligence-Generated Content in Political Advertisements as soon as is possible in view of the risks that AI generated political content poses to our democracy. 

We have already seen political campaigns create and disseminate disinformation with the aid of Artificial Intelligence in an attempt to deceive the electorate. Disinformation threatens the ability of citizens to cast their vote fully aware of the policies and consequences of voting for a particular candidate.  High quality AI-generated deep fakes can seriously mislead the electorate by misrepresenting what politicians, and others, say or do. It is vital that a clear, highly visible disclosure accompanies any political advertisement that uses AI in whole or in part. 

The FCC's proposal is an important step in providing transparency and integrity to our elections and our democratic process. This proposal can make a huge difference in the odds of survival of our democracy.

