12 Police Dep’t of Chicago v. Mosle, 408 U.S. 92, 95 (1972) (emphasis added).
13 Reed v. Town of Gilbert, 576 U.S. 155, 163–64 (2015).
14 Nat’l Inst. of Family & Life Advocates v. Becerra, 585 U.S. 755, 766 (2018) (“Becerra”); All speech is presumptively protected
