2176,10919212704793,2024-09-19T16:58:24.151Z,Rodney Sims,,,"Greetings:

I am asking the FCC to adopt its proposal on the Disclosure and Transparency of Artificial Intelligence-Generated Content in Political Advertisements as soon as possible.

Given recent advances in artificial intelligence, I’m concerned that candidates and issue campaigners will have an open invitation to deceive voters unless you step in. An attempt has already occurred during this presidential election cycle with Taylor Swift being the victim. High quality deep fakes can realistically depict people saying or doing things that did not occur. By requiring a clear disclosure every time AI is used to make an ad, you can prevent political actors from deceiving the public.

Your proposal is a strong step to ensure transparency and the integrity of our democratic process. Please adopt it without delay. Thank you for your time and consideration.

Respectfully,",877
