17, 2023, https://www.politico.com/news/2023/07/17/desantis-pac-ai-generated-trump-in-ad-00106695;
35 See, e.g., McConnell, 540 U.S. at 196; Citizens United v. FEC, 558 U.S. 310, 368–71 (2010).
36 See, e.g., Second Report and Order, FCC 12-44, https://docs.fcc.gov/public/attachments/FCC-12-44A1.pdf.
37 The Leadership Conference on Civil and Human Rights (The Leadership Conference), Common Cause, United
