educating consumers to make informed decisions about where they consume and disseminate news and
information.)
71 Am. Meat Inst. v. U.S. Dep’t of Agric., 760 F.3d 18, 31 (D.C. Cir. 2014) (Kavanaugh, J., concurring); see also
