be more than the satisfaction of mere ‘consumer curiosity’”); Int’l Dairy Foods Ass’n v. Amestoy, 92 F.3d 67, 73 (2d
Cir. 1996) (“We are aware of no case in which consumer interest alone was sufficient[.]”).
72 NPRM ¶ 31.
