of technology, including AI” to accomplish a fraudulent misrepresentation.10 Accordingly, the
FEC has clarified that it will be policing the use of AI in this context. Moreover, even while FEC
action on AI has been pending, many states also have begun to regulate AI in political advertising.
Like the FEC, the states generally have acted by imposing their regulatory requirements directly
